thread.title: BRIEF-Laan & Spar Bank FY Net Interest Income Rises To DKK 759.8 Million

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Laan & Spar Bank FY Net Interest Income Rises To DKK 759.8 Million
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - LAAN & SPAR BANK A/S:
* FY NET INTEREST INCOME DKK 759.8 ‍​ MILLION VERSUS DKK 746.2 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY NET INCOME DKK 170.2 ‍​ MILLION VERSUS DKK 138.9 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY LOAN LOSSES DKK 18.6‍​ MILLION VERSUS DKK 29.5 MILLION YEAR AGO
* EXPECTS 2018 RESULTS AFTER TAX IN THE RANGE OF DKK 120-150 MILLION
* BOARD PROPOSES DIVIDEND DKK 10 PER SHARE FOR 2017 VERSUS DKK 8 PER SHARE IN 2016‍​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
